# Zurvan Linux — §1 Core System & Base Utilities
# (package-manifest.md §1)
# Explicit kernel package required for iso-hybrid boot; live-build does
# not auto-install a kernel when --debian-installer none is used.
# The kernel package is supplied by the arch-conditional kernel list
# written by CI: kernel-amd64.list.chroot or kernel-arm64.list.chroot.
